post.body: With the holidays over, I think it finally will. Maybe in a week or so it'll be totally gone.
Well, that is 11 total since Xmas day, but still. A lot.
LOL they sure love to take the money, for sure.
Ooh okay. What all has to be done there?
Well at least you'll get to rest tomorrow and Wednesday.
Are you working tomorrow, too?
Oh I am sure you were. Gotta be rough going back to that schedule after all that time off.
I miss yoooooou!
Aw that's too bad, I really love that show.
ever see How's It Made on the Science Channel? I find it fascinating. Many people find it a bit boring though.
A bit. Luckily, one of my fav shows comes on in 30 minutes so I won't be stuck with infomercials, yay!
I've done smoothies and they are good except for the occasional chunk of ice that hadn't been mashed too well, haha.
LOL I actually have a Magic Bullet and while it doesn't work as well as they say, it is pretty awesome. I use it all the time.
TV is so bad this weekend, I am watching "A Very Brady Sequel" ......the fuck.
11 family members sick and counting. Holy hell, lmao.
I haven't played Tetris in DAYS. What on Earth is wrong with me?!
My puppy is so damn cute I can't even stand it, sometimes.
Bored enough to be reading about the Duggars. Lulz.
I'm sure I look like an idiot, spraying myself down with Lysol and doing through a bottle of hand sanitizer by myself in 1 weekend.
Hmm. Watcing some show about Cruises on Travel Channel. Doesn't look like I'll be taking a cruise in my lifetime. Nope.
